# RxJs Tutorial:
    The RxJs is a library of JavaScript and it full is Reactive Extension for JavScript and it was used to 
    habdle the async function and handle the bunch of API calls using the Reactive Programming.

# Inportant Topics:
    1. Observable:
        The observable is an Class and it was received the first parameter as a callback function and
        this callback receives the observer as an object to emit the each and every value of the infinite
        Array values from API call or from async function.

    2. Observer
        It's an object containing the bunch of methods to handle the emitted value from the Observable.

    3. Subscription

    4. Subject

    5. Operator
        1. map
        2. filter
        3. reduce
        4. every 
    
    6. Schedulers